4,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:24:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0857d555521aee8dec020fb34debe10eb775489b","tid":1532724,"uid":36470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:26:10.000Z","msg":"幾時播Animal Farm"},{"pid":"8d89a05f362d9fd53787811076b757e1e929b133","tid":1532724,"uid":16034,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:29:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講幾句難聽說話<br />\n見到大家播固然係歡迎，但唔好再將香港同烏克蘭掛勾，我地唔配。<br />\n見到有人打曬飛機講香港係summer on fire真係忍唔住笑，斬隻狗放個火都要傳卧底論，見到幾隻速龍黎就散水唔敢還拖，見到手足比人禁低就自己跑快啲無諗要救，成日就話咩唔好送頭唔好流血，仲學人叫光復香港時代革命？<br />\n屌你有無諗過，作為平民又點可能同班狗同等裝備，除左人數同流血覺悟，無野可以拎黎對抗班狗，唔好話咩對準政權，狗就係政權手中既盾，你唔撚打爆個盾就想打個政權，咁撚天真架咩？<br />\n歐美固然可以幫拖，但憑咩野人地要放棄利益黎幫你？永遠將成敗交托係人地手上，呢樣野真係好香港人style，總有班人係IG FB係咁怒屌黎呃like，但真係要上場就多多理由，交比其他人付出啦，成功就共享成果。"},{"pid":"6632617f2cac62f7c440b91e7662cfde9a40d5af","tid":1532724,"uid":35249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:30:45.000Z","msg":"睇曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40d081d8576519a5f5738f102f98be9891b4b673","tid":1532724,"uid":78222,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:31:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.sharegif.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/1-014.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sharegif.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F05%2F1-014.gif&h=3ff6fbed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.sharegif.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/1-024.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sharegif.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F05%2F1-024.gif&h=067bc728&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6173cdf68862a5ba840ad9f0393f0aa827b156f8","tid":1532724,"uid":48187,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:33:24.000Z","msg":"我發現好多後生都未睇過，呢套堅係抗爭入門，啲句子好有用！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2082a760140e9b24b46794ee339118081dd4fd8e","tid":1532724,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9905b4493db93ca92eb44c89b63ad3bffa15e00f","tid":1532724,"uid":50216,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"690d7ea5a542c86ba702794415d964dea8f52431","tid":1532724,"uid":119756,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:30:46.000Z","msg":"逆權公民會唔會好d <br />\n同宜家情況好似<br />\n市民好易有共鳴"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:05:14.000Z","msg":"viutv今個星期六播"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:44:44.000Z","msg":"有良心電視台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d89763a410414b1776d7f8ca9711ead56ee08bdf","tid":1532724,"uid":33104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0857d555521aee8dec020fb34debe10eb775489b","tid":1532724,"uid":36470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:26:10.000Z","msg":"幾時播Animal Farm"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:48:25.000Z","msg":"睇完要做背景同內容解說"},{"pid":"f66e45c52ab87ba126a7b106917306d008f3709b","tid":1532724,"uid":64078,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:59:46.000Z","msg":"好老實，唔建議播v煞，因為佢其實係superhero戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n戲入面成功關鍵就係V, 現實中唔會有V, 唔會有刀槍不入既超人幫，靠既就只有我地香港人<br />\n要播就播逆權律師"},{"pid":"0b6e100bda943eebe271741ad301786f4a799c21","tid":1532724,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:01:07.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要堅持下去，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"},{"pid":"4630d7d1682ff15d809c13df5b843d5264328061","tid":1532724,"uid":50882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0857d555521aee8dec020fb34debe10eb775489b","tid":1532724,"uid":36470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:26:10.000Z","msg":"幾時播Animal Farm"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:12:51.000Z","msg":"1984適合d"},{"pid":"95b96cb2e39c062a6cc8c73f4df2d93c1133b4f8","tid":1532724,"uid":34869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f66e45c52ab87ba126a7b106917306d008f3709b","tid":1532724,"uid":64078,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:59:46.000Z","msg":"好老實，唔建議播v煞，因為佢其實係superhero戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n戲入面成功關鍵就係V, 現實中唔會有V, 唔會有刀槍不入既超人幫，靠既就只有我地香港人<br />\n要播就播逆權律師"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:25:13.000Z","msg":"V煞最後回歸大眾人人出黎, 同時V煞中槍死自爆, 呢D畫面其實係比大家諗真係有人犧牲既情況 (我覺得好快會出現)<br />\n<br />\n不過播其他片都ok, 最緊要係個個星期有片睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ecb2ef87701bcc48f50b2faa4c62e49d6cd544d","tid":1532724,"uid":36470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d89763a410414b1776d7f8ca9711ead